# Privacy Policy for Spirit Level App

Louis Pretorius built the Spirit Level app as a free app. This SERVICE is provided by Louis Pretorius at no cost and is intended for use as is.

This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use our Service.

The app does not collect, store, or share any personal data from users.

### Changes to This Privacy Policy
I may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes.

